# persona/ — Persona Dimension Computers
# format: ctx/1.0
# last-verified: 2026-03-26
# edges: -> call/render | ~> subscribe/read

## Brand Persona — Jewelry Store
  BrandEmotionalComputer : Mood from customer signals [service]
    -> DimensionComputer, EmotionalState
  BrandLinguisticComputer : Fixed jewelry brand voice [service]
    -> DimensionComputer, LinguisticState
  BrandRelationalComputer : Product KG entity detection [service]
    -> DimensionComputer, RelationalState
    ~> JewelryKG, sqlite3
  BrandTemporalComputer : Customer journey stages [service]
    -> DimensionComputer, TemporalState

## Therapy Persona — Mental Wellbeing
  TherapyEmotionalComputer : Empathy from KG concerns [service]
    -> DimensionComputer, EmotionalState
    ~> TherapyKG
  TherapyLinguisticComputer : Adaptive therapeutic voice [service]
    -> DimensionComputer, LinguisticState
    ~> TherapyKG
  TherapyRelationalComputer : Therapy KG subgraph activation [service]
    -> DimensionComputer, RelationalState
    ~> TherapyKG
  TherapyTemporalComputer : Session arc and handoff [service]
    -> DimensionComputer, TemporalState
    ~> TherapyKG

## persona_engine Framework
  DimensionComputer : Base class for all computers [lib] @entry
  EmotionalState : X-axis return type [type]
  LinguisticState : Z-axis return type [type]
  RelationalState : Y-axis return type [type]
  TemporalState : T-axis return type [type]

## Knowledge Graphs
  JewelryKG : SQLite product graph [data]
  TherapyKG : User's personal graph [data]

## External
  sqlite3 : Database access [ext]
